---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const seo = {
  version: '2026-03-23-ui-test-editorial',
  pageType: 'C',
  entityKey: 'amara-brand',
  languages: {
    en: {
      title: 'AMARA Editorial Test',
      description: 'Editorial trust page design test.',
      robots: 'noindex, nofollow',
      canonical: 'auto'
    }
  }
};
---

<BaseLayout seo={seo}>
  <div class="am-editorial-test">
    <div class="am-editorial-test__wrap">
      <main class="am-editorial-test__main">
        <section class="am-editorial-test__hero">
          <span class="am-editorial-test__kicker">AMARA</span>
          <h1 class="am-editorial-test__title">AMARA &mdash; Holiday Apartments in Andalusia</h1>
          <p class="am-editorial-test__lead">Frigiliana &middot; Nerja &middot; Tarifa</p>
          <p class="am-editorial-test__intro">
            You arrive, open the door, and feel immediate relief.
            Everything is prepared. Nothing asks for attention.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="am-editorial-test__section">
          <h2 class="am-editorial-test__section-title">AMARA means love</h2>
          <div class="am-editorial-test__flow">
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              AMARA means love. Love for the details. Love for what we do.
              A kind of love that stays &mdash; because it&apos;s consistent, not loud.
            </p>
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              AMARA was built from years of travel and hosting experience &mdash; professional and personal &mdash; with one clear goal: a stay that feels effortless from the first minute.
            </p>
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              This name is not a promise for a moment. It is a promise for what remains afterwards: trust, return guests, and the feeling of having truly arrived.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="am-editorial-test__section">
          <h2 class="am-editorial-test__section-title">About us? Actually: about you.</h2>
          <div class="am-editorial-test__flow">
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              Everything at AMARA is built around the guest. Not around trends. Not around platform logic. Not around short-term optimisation.
            </p>
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              Hosting here is a matter of trust. The guiding question is always: What makes this stay genuinely better for the guest?
            </p>
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              That question guides every decision &mdash; consistency, responsibility, and long-term guest satisfaction.
            </p>
          </div>
          <blockquote class="am-editorial-test__quote">
            &ldquo;Everything was exactly as described &mdash; even better when we arrived.&rdquo;
          </blockquote>
        </section>

        <section class="am-editorial-test__section">
          <h2 class="am-editorial-test__section-title">What we do differently</h2>
          <div class="am-editorial-test__list">
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              <strong>Prepared for real stays</strong><br />
              Comfort and daily usefulness first &mdash; not staged for photos.
            </p>
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              <strong>Consistency over promises</strong><br />
              What you see is what you find &mdash; every season, every stay.
            </p>
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              <strong>Calm, not stimulation</strong><br />
              Design supports rest &mdash; not visual noise.
            </p>
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              <strong>Direct responsibility</strong><br />
              You communicate with the people responsible for your stay.
            </p>
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              <strong>Privacy respected</strong><br />
              Present when needed, invisible otherwise.
            </p>
          </div>
          <p class="am-editorial-test__body am-editorial-test__body--closing">
            These choices are intentional. They are also not for everyone &mdash; and that is exactly the point.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="am-editorial-test__section">
          <h2 class="am-editorial-test__section-title">Honest quality in every AMARA home</h2>
          <div class="am-editorial-test__list">
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              <strong>Deep sleep</strong><br />
              High-quality mattresses, crisp linens, quiet nights.
            </p>
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              <strong>Cleanliness (non-negotiable)</strong><br />
              Thorough preparation &mdash; never rushed, never &ldquo;good enough&rdquo;.
            </p>
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              <strong>Materials that age well</strong><br />
              Durable choices instead of quick fixes.
            </p>
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              <strong>Reliable equipment</strong><br />
              Useful details, not showroom gimmicks.
            </p>
          </div>
          <p class="am-editorial-test__body am-editorial-test__body--closing">
            If something no longer meets our standards, it is replaced &mdash; quietly, consistently, without discussion.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="am-editorial-test__section">
          <h2 class="am-editorial-test__section-title">Stable pricing. No discounts.</h2>
          <div class="am-editorial-test__flow">
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              AMARA is not the cheapest option &mdash; and it is not designed to be. Reliable quality, care, and continuous reinvestment have real costs.
            </p>
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              Pricing is stable, transparent, and intentional &mdash; without flash deals or artificial promotions.
            </p>
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              If you are looking for the lowest price, AMARA is not the right fit.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="am-editorial-test__section">
          <h2 class="am-editorial-test__section-title">Our locations in Andalusia</h2>
          <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
            Each AMARA location is chosen for atmosphere, rhythm, and the kind of stay it makes possible.
          </p>
          <div class="am-editorial-test__location-list">
            <div class="am-editorial-test__location-item">
              <h3 class="am-editorial-test__location-title">Frigiliana</h3>
              <p class="am-editorial-test__body">Quiet depth, white village calm, and a sense of time.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="am-editorial-test__location-item">
              <h3 class="am-editorial-test__location-title">Nerja</h3>
              <p class="am-editorial-test__body">Sea rhythm, authentic energy &mdash; with balance and ease.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="am-editorial-test__location-item">
              <h3 class="am-editorial-test__location-title">Tarifa</h3>
              <p class="am-editorial-test__body">Wide horizons, light and wind &mdash; active outdoors, calm indoors.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="am-editorial-test__section">
          <h2 class="am-editorial-test__section-title">Your host</h2>
          <p class="am-editorial-test__host-name">Robert &mdash; Founder &amp; Host</p>
          <div class="am-editorial-test__list">
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              <strong>Fast replies</strong><br />
              Clear, direct, reliable communication.
            </p>
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              <strong>Present, not intrusive</strong><br />
              Reachable when needed, invisible otherwise.
            </p>
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              <strong>Languages</strong><br />
              DE &middot; EN &middot; ES
            </p>
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              <strong>Insider guidance</strong><br />
              Curated recommendations for calm, authentic experiences.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="am-editorial-test__section">
          <h2 class="am-editorial-test__section-title">A small team. One standard.</h2>
          <div class="am-editorial-test__list">
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              <strong>Small and trusted</strong><br />
              A team that shares the same standards.
            </p>
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              <strong>The same every stay</strong><br />
              Care applied consistently &mdash; not selectively.
            </p>
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              <strong>Quiet execution</strong><br />
              Quality happens in the background &mdash; so the stay feels effortless.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="am-editorial-test__section">
          <h2 class="am-editorial-test__section-title">AMARA Earth</h2>
          <div class="am-editorial-test__flow">
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">Sustainable by choice.</p>
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              Sustainability at AMARA means practical decisions that reduce impact without reducing comfort.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="am-editorial-test__list">
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              <strong>Energy</strong><br />
              Solar hot water &middot; Renewable electricity &middot; LED lighting &middot; Efficient appliances
            </p>
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              <strong>Water &amp; waste</strong><br />
              Low-flow showers &middot; Recycling &middot; Refillable amenities &middot; No capsule coffee systems
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="am-editorial-test__cta">
          <h2 class="am-editorial-test__section-title">If you value reliability, you&apos;ll feel at home here</h2>
          <div class="am-editorial-test__flow">
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              AMARA is for guests who appreciate calm execution, honest communication, and places that feel considered rather than staged.
            </p>
            <p class="am-editorial-test__body">
              Many guests return &mdash; because expectations are met, quietly and consistently.
            </p>
          </div>
          <p class="am-editorial-test__cta-links">
            <a href="#">Check availability</a>
            <span>&middot;</span>
            <a href="#">Guest reviews</a>
            <span>&middot;</span>
            <a href="#">Direct booking benefits</a>
          </p>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .am-editorial-test {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: clamp(4.5rem, 8vw, 7rem) 1.5rem 5rem;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(189, 134, 91, 0.12), transparent 34%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 250, 244, 0.82), rgba(248, 242, 233, 0.92) 55%, rgba(244, 237, 228, 0.98));
  }

  .am-editorial-test__wrap {
    max-width: 74rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .am-editorial-test__main {
    max-width: 43rem;
  }

  .am-editorial-test__hero {
    padding: 0 0 3.75rem;
    margin: 0 0 4.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(65, 52, 41, 0.12);
  }

  .am-editorial-test__kicker {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #8f5f37;
  }

  .am-editorial-test__title,
  .am-editorial-test__section-title,
  .am-editorial-test__location-title,
  .am-editorial-test__host-name,
  .am-editorial-test__quote {
    font-family: "Newsreader", Georgia, serif;
  }

  .am-editorial-test__title {
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    font-size: clamp(3.15rem, 8vw, 5.7rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #231812;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .am-editorial-test__lead {
    margin: 0 0 0.85rem;
    font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.08rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    color: rgba(35, 24, 18, 0.68);
  }

  .am-editorial-test__intro {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 30rem;
    font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2vw, 1.35rem);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: #2f241c;
  }

  .am-editorial-test__section,
  .am-editorial-test__cta {
    margin-bottom: 4.75rem;
  }

  .am-editorial-test__section-title {
    margin: 0 0 1.6rem;
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw, 3.7rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 0.98;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #231812;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .am-editorial-test__flow,
  .am-editorial-test__list,
  .am-editorial-test__location-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.35rem;
  }

  .am-editorial-test__location-list {
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 1.6rem;
  }

  .am-editorial-test__location-item {
    padding-top: 1.35rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(65, 52, 41, 0.09);
  }

  .am-editorial-test__location-item:first-child {
    padding-top: 0;
    border-top: 0;
  }

  .am-editorial-test__location-title {
    margin: 0 0 0.45rem;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: #231812;
  }

  .am-editorial-test__host-name {
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.7rem;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #231812;
  }

  .am-editorial-test__body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: rgba(35, 24, 18, 0.82);
  }

  .am-editorial-test__body strong {
    color: #231812;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .am-editorial-test__body--closing {
    margin-top: 1.6rem;
    color: rgba(35, 24, 18, 0.74);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .am-editorial-test__quote {
    margin: 2rem 0 0;
    padding: 0.25rem 0 0.25rem 1.35rem;
    border-left: 1px solid rgba(143, 95, 55, 0.3);
    font-size: clamp(1.55rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #2a1e17;
  }

  .am-editorial-test__cta {
    padding-top: 2.2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(65, 52, 41, 0.12);
  }

  .am-editorial-test__cta-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.55rem 0.9rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin: 1.75rem 0 0;
    font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .am-editorial-test__cta-links span {
    color: rgba(35, 24, 18, 0.45);
  }

  .am-editorial-test__cta-links a {
    color: #2a1e17;
    text-decoration-line: underline;
    text-decoration-thickness: 1px;
    text-underline-offset: 0.22em;
    text-decoration-color: rgba(65, 52, 41, 0.22);
    transition: color 160ms ease, text-decoration-color 160ms ease;
  }

  .am-editorial-test__cta-links a:hover {
    color: #8f5f37;
    text-decoration-color: rgba(143, 95, 55, 0.35);
  }

  @media (max-width: 48rem) {
    .am-editorial-test {
      padding: 4rem 1.1rem 4.5rem;
    }

    .am-editorial-test__hero {
      margin-bottom: 3.75rem;
      padding-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .am-editorial-test__section,
    .am-editorial-test__cta {
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .am-editorial-test__body,
    .am-editorial-test__intro {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
  }
</style>
